; Coverage for annotate.cc value expression in annotation

2024/01/01 Buy
    Assets:Stock     10 AAPL {$100} ((market(amount, date, t)))
    Assets:Cash

test reg Assets:Stock --lots --lot-notes
24-Jan-01 Buy                   Assets:Stock           10 AAPL {$100} ((market(amount, date, t))) 10 AAPL {$100} ((market(amount, date, t)))
end test
